smart_mirror/
├── main.py                 # Central router / main loop
├── requirements.txt        # Libraries for all team members
├── .env                    # API keys and secrets
├── modules/
│   ├── gui/
│   │   ├── layout.py       # Layout zones (Rory)
│   │   ├── render.py       # Rendering modules (Rory)
│   │   └── display.py      # Fullscreen mirror display (Rory)
│   ├── state/
│   │   └── state_manager.py # State manager (Rory)
│   ├── timer/
│   │   └── timer_backend.py # Timer backend (Rorik)
│   ├── calendar/
│   │   └── calendar_data.py # Calendar data (Rorik)
│   ├── media/
│   │   └── media_playback.py # Music/video playback (Rorik)
│   ├── voice/
│   │   ├── elevenlabs.py    # Voice reply / ElevenLabs (Justin)
│   │   └── router.py        # Intent router / integration (Justin)
│   └── audio/
│       ├── mic_input.py     # Mic capture (Estefania)
│       ├── speech_to_text.py # Convert audio to text (Estefania)
│       └── weather.py       # Weather API (Estefania)

Rory (GUI work and state):
- Layout zones, rendering modules, fullscreen display
- Manages state_manager.py for current weather, timer, calendar, music
- Reads state from backend modules and displays it

Rorik (Backend logic):
- Timer backend, calendar data, media playback
- Updates state that Rory’s GUI reads
- Media playback may be triggered by router (Justin)

Justin (Voice integration):
- Handles ElevenLabs responses, converts router commands to voice
- Runs router that connects voice input, GUI updates, timers, media playback

Estefania (Input and APIs):
- Captures mic input
- Converts speech → text
- Fetches weather data (can mock for MVP)
- Provides parsed info to router → state → GUI

Rory (GUI work and state):
- layout.py: Define screen zones for time, weather, calendar, timer.
- render.py: Draw each module’s content on the screen.
- display.py: OpenCV fullscreen display.
- state_manager.py: Store current values for weather, timer, calendar, music.

Rorik (Backend logic):
- timer_backend.py: Start/stop timers, track remaining time.
- calendar_data.py: Provide events (MVP can be hardcoded).
- media_playback.py: Play/stop music and videos.

Justin (Voice integration):
- elevenlabs.py: Speak responses from the system.
- router.py: Receive intents → call the appropriate backend module → update state.

Estefania (Input and APIs):
- mic_input.py: Record audio from user.
- speech_to_text.py: Convert audio → text.
- weather.py: Fetch weather data from API (or mock for MVP).
